# Project Context

NASA interplanetary fuel calculator (NEX Energy challenge). **See [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for all domain rules, WS contract, acceptance tests, and commands.**

## Non-negotiable boundaries

- Fuel logic → `packages/fuel-core` only
- Types/domain constants → `packages/shared`
- Validation + error messages → `apps/server`
- UI only → `apps/client` (no fuel formulas)
- Real-time WebSocket, no submit button
